            {
                "box": {
                    "code": "// from the ease package, pow changed from 2 to 1.93 to better match Moog MF-101S filter freq taper\r\n\r\n// Based on Warren Moore's easing C source code\r\n// https://github.com/warrenm/AHEasing/blob/master/AHEasing/easing.c\r\n\r\n// Modeled after the exponential function y = 2^(10(x - 1))\r\n\nExponentialEaseIn(value)\n{\n\treturn (value == 0.0) ? value : pow(1.93, 10 * (value - 1));\n}\r\n\r\nout1 = ExponentialEaseIn(in1);\r\n\r\n",
                    "fontface": 0,
                    "fontname": "<Monospaced>",
                    "fontsize": 12.0,
